{"tid":86773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他有 3 個爸媽，烏克蘭生殖技術再突破","createTime":"2017-01-19T10:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T11:23:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"966c8bbc7b73d48acba06b56f2c79593bf985e4e","tid":86773,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/11522188665_0c397ede99_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F11522188665_0c397ede99_z.jpg&h=06ad9ba1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n透過新技術的使用，烏克蘭首都基輔一家生育診所院長今天表示，該診所誕生一名擁有 3 名父母 DNA 的男嬰。 <br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，基輔的納基亞（Nadiya）私人生育診所院長朱金（Valeriy Zukin）指出，這名男嬰除了接受來自父母的 DNA，還利用一種稱為原核轉移（Pronuclear Transfer）的技術，獲得卵子捐贈者的基因。朱金告訴法新社：「這是全球第一名利用原核轉移技術誕生的嬰兒。」 <br />\n<br />\n該診所聲明指出，34 歲的母親於 1 月 5 日產下這名健康的男嬰，過去她試過多次試管嬰兒，超過 15 年求子未果。 <br />\n<br />\n這項技術將母親已受精的卵子細胞核，注入捐贈者移除掉細胞核的卵子中。如此一來，這個受精卵整體上除了擁有來自父母的 DNA，同時還有少量、約 0.15% 的卵子捐贈者 DNA。 <br />\n<br />\n這名男嬰被視為全球第 2 名擁有「3 父母」的嬰兒，2016 年在墨西哥，已有一名嬰兒透過不同技術出生。 <br />\n<br />\n（譯者：許湘欣；首圖來源：Flickr/Jens Bergander CC BY 2.0）"},{"pid":"ee87dacd303d99c066fdba96c996eea2cd03763e","tid":86773,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aefe86032d8d5bba41f7ddfe9d9e6ba58df2126","tid":86773,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bea315c3cb19efe0c46f55f1344829635a7e35","tid":86773,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"上帝"},{"pid":"ef8b636a8d284b2f48b6a5c356b11cea96cfcc7a","tid":86773,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}